&lt;h2 id=&#34;final-thoughts&#34;&gt;Final Thoughts&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The challenge is over and we are very, very happy about the great success! Thank you everyone for participating in our challenge with a total of &lt;strong&gt;1,960 contributions&lt;/strong&gt; (and more are still coming in while people are catching up). On the first day, we had the all-time record of 135 contributions!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/img/chart-challenge/timeseries_category.png&#34; style=&#34;height: 100%; width: 100%; object-fit: contain;&#34;&gt;
